msgctxt "56_Kiryu"
msgid "You're one of the Dark Clan?"
msgstr "You're one of the Dark Clan?"

msgctxt "68_Man with Dark Clan"
msgid "My name is Blanc. You are Kiryu?"
msgstr "My name is Blanc. You are Kiryu?"

msgctxt "80_Kiryu"
msgid "Right. And I'm guessing you're not Japanese?"
msgstr "Right. And I'm guessing you're not Japanese?"

msgctxt "92_Blanc"
msgid "Korean."
msgstr "Korean."

msgctxt "104_Kiryu"
msgid "Korean, huh? A while back, I had some trouble with a group called the Jingweon Mafia. You from the mafia, too?"
msgstr "Korean, huh? A while back, I had some trouble with a group called the Jingweon Mafia. You from the mafia, too?"

msgctxt "116_Blanc"
msgid "Not anymore. In Japan, mafia is weak. Dark Clan is better."
msgstr "Not anymore. In Japan, mafia is weak. Dark Clan is better."

msgctxt "128_Kiryu"
msgid "Who's giving you your orders?"
msgstr "Who's giving you your orders?"

msgctxt "140_Blanc"
msgid "Can not tell. But you, die. Is your fate."
msgstr "Can not tell. But you, die. Is your fate."

msgctxt "152_Kiryu"
msgid "What do I have to do with anything?"
msgstr "What do I have to do with anything?"

msgctxt "164_Blanc"
msgid "Power balance not good when you are here. Not good for Kamurocho. So they call me."
msgstr "Power balance not good when you are here. Not good for Kamurocho. So they call me."

msgctxt "176_Kiryu"
msgid "Balance? What balance?"
msgstr "Balance? What balance?"

msgctxt "188_Blanc"
msgid "You die, balance is okay."
msgstr "You die, balance is okay."

